snippet.title: Neebota: 99 Fails Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1659250/Neebota_99_Fails/

Precision platforming with multiple genre-bending mechanics in Zeebo's surreal nightmare. Addictively easy to play, very difficult to master. Find out the source of Zeebo's torture by analyzing his dream journal as you progress.
